</廢止註記>
<沿革內容><![CDATA[1.Promulgated on May, 28, 2008]]></沿革內容>
<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The pay of the President and the Vice President shall be regulated by this act.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The following terms shall have the meaning set forth below:
1. Monthly salary: refers to the basic pay in accordance to this act.
2. Political affairs pay: refers to the additional pay for the duty of the post holder in addition to the monthly salary.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The pay of the President and the Vice President shall be divided into monthly salary and political affairs pay, which shall be given monthly.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The monthly salary of the President and the Vice President shall be given in accordance to the following standards:
1. The monthly salary of the President shall be given as 2,700 points.
2. The monthly salary of the Vice President shall be given as 2,000 points.
The Executive Yuan shall regulate the method for converting the points correspondent to the pay amount for the monthly pay set forth above.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The amount of political affairs pay shall be regulated by the Executive Yuan.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 6</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The enactment date of this Act shall be regulated by the Executive Yuan.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
